			<Item class="StringValue" referent="RBXafc9e12ed55440dab4d4bc04e45ca840">
				<Properties>
					<string name="Value"><![CDATA[Current prototype is still inside Roblox Studio scripts.

Important live scripts:
- ServerScriptService/Services/WOBGameplayServer
- ServerScriptService/Services/WOBDummyRespawnServer
- ServerScriptService/Services/WOBProjectileVisualEnhancer
- StarterPlayer/StarterPlayerScripts/WOBClientController
- StarterGui/HUD/WOBHudController

Later repository structure:
- README.md
- AGENTS.md
- docs/GDD_ROBLOX.md
- docs/ARCHITECTURE.md
- src/ReplicatedStorage/Shared
- src/ServerScriptService/Services
- src/StarterPlayer/StarterPlayerScripts
]]></string>
